  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个OTT视频平台的状态流转图，核心是用户怎么从连接服务到最终看视频。起点应该是用户连接到OTT系统，然后可以创建房间或者加入已有房间，最后才能使用OTT观看视频。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Connect",
        "CreateRoom",
        "JoinRoom",
        "UseOTT",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。我注意到您提到了起点，那这个图需要一个明确的初始状态吗？另外，HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine是作为一个外部系统存在，还是也需要作为状态节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "Connect"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine不是用户状态，它是整个流程的上下文引擎，可以把它放在图外侧作为隐含的支撑系统。用户连接OTT时受它影响，使用OTT看完视频后数据也要回流给它。所以让它和Connect、UseOTT这两个节点有连线，但不用做成状态节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "Connect",
        "UseOTT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把四个用户状态画出来：Connect（用户连接到OTT）、CreateRoom（创建房间）、JoinRoom（加入房间）、UseOTT（使用OTT观看视频）。然后让HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine从左侧指向Connect，形成入口关联。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Connect",
        "CreateRoom",
        "JoinRoom",
        "UseOTT",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，Connect作为入口很合理。接下来Connect之后用户应该有两个选择：要么CreateRoom创建新房间，要么JoinRoom加入别人创建的房间。这两个动作都直接从Connect引出。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Connect",
        "CreateRoom",
        "JoinRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：Connect指向CreateRoom，Connect也指向JoinRoom。那CreateRoom和JoinRoom之间需要连线吗？比如创建完房间自动加入？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Connect",
        "CreateRoom",
        "JoinRoom"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "需要，CreateRoom之后用户自然进入那个房间，所以CreateRoom要连到JoinRoom。然后JoinRoom之后才能UseOTT，这个顺序不能变——必须先有房间才能看视频。最后UseOTT结束要把观看数据返回给HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine，形成闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CreateRoom",
        "JoinRoom",
        "UseOTT",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。现在结构是：HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine指向Connect作为入口，Connect分出CreateRoom和JoinRoom，CreateRoom流向JoinRoom，JoinRoom再到UseOTT，最后UseOTT指回HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine形成闭环。您看还有什么需要调整的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine",
        "Connect",
        "CreateRoom",
        "JoinRoom",
        "UseOTT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题，这个流转逻辑准确反映了我们的业务流程。HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine作为外部引擎贯穿始终，用户状态从连接到最终观看形成完整路径，可以定稿了。",
      "elements_involved": [
